# Your Current Sell Rule

You already defined:

| Market Type        |       Sell Trigger |
| ------------------ | -----------------: |
| Normal market      | +25% basket profit |
| Euphoric/parabolic | +20% basket profit |

Meaning:

If accumulated ETF basket value becomes:

Current\ Value \ge Invested\ Amount \times 1.25

then:

* sell full basket,
* book profit,
* restart cycle.

This is already a strong framework.

