# Important Insight

The sell rule is actually MORE important than buy rule.

Why?

Most investors:

* know how to buy,
* don’t know when to exit.

Without exits:

* volatility harvesting becomes permanent holding,
* capital rotation slows,
* CAGR falls.

Your sell trigger is what converts:

> volatility into compounding.
